    <item>
      <title>EQ2: Bugbears always roll need</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/2009/04/10/eq2-bugbears-always-roll-need/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Apr 2009 07:40:41 -0500</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/2009/04/10/eq2-bugbears-always-roll-need/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://chasingdings.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/04/bugbearsneed.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Kobold and Bugbear discuss asshattery&#34; title=&#34;bugbearsneed&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;No matter how many times you tell the Bugbear that the guild isn&amp;rsquo;t raiding for his &lt;em&gt;alt&lt;/em&gt;, he still rolls need on absolutely everything.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The EQ2 Station Marketplace added a couple of new items today. The Bugbear joins the Kobold, Orc, and some creepy elves as the newest denizen of your apartment or guild hall.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Personality-wise, Bugbear isn&amp;rsquo;t the best team player. If you&amp;rsquo;re not in his tribe, then you&amp;rsquo;re nothing. And if you DO happen to be a Bugbear &amp;ndash; &lt;em&gt;from his tribe&lt;/em&gt; &amp;ndash; well, he&amp;rsquo;s more important than you, and the elders like him more, and they wanted him to have this thing.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>EQ2: Epic encounter in my bedroom</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/2009/04/05/eq2-epic-encounter-in-my-bedroom/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 05 Apr 2009 22:19:44 -0500</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/2009/04/05/eq2-epic-encounter-in-my-bedroom/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;It was really cool! See, Kasul and I were kinda bored, and we were alone in the guild hall, and we got to thinking about what we could do and so we &amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;HEY! STOP SNIGGERING!&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;OMG! You people&amp;hellip; I swear. I&amp;rsquo;m gonna stop writing this post unless you stop laughing.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;It wasn&amp;rsquo;t THAT kind of encounter.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://chasingdings.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/04/everquest2-2009-04-04-21-58-41-05.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;everquest2-2009-04-04-21-58-41-05&#34; title=&#34;everquest2-2009-04-04-21-58-41-05&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;A couple of weeks ago, SOE put an Orc Centurion into their Station Marketplace thingy RMT thing. And I&amp;rsquo;ve been wracking my brains trying to think of what you could DO with it.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
